# JavaScript Calculator

A simple calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features
- Addition (+)
- Subtraction (-)
- Multiplication (×)
- Division (÷)
- Percentage (%)
- Clear (C)
- Responsive UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## What I Learned
- DOM Manipulation
- Event Handling
- JavaScript Variables
- Debugging
- Building interactive web applications
